My parents have given me the privilege to jot some notes on myself to help you to get some traces of me and not completely me. 

Understanding about someone can never be accomplished fully, so kindly do not try to draw any conclusion about a person out of his/her profile. People find me as a fun lover and everyone loves to chat with me. That's because, I am a good listener and I intend to reciprocate in their own language which usually cherishes them. I always try to explore and create my own lovely world, where I have also learnt to enjoy from my loneliness and I prefer it sometimes. I love to pull my brothers leg and we have been always very supportive to each other at all circumstances. My father is equally a fun loving person, but yet known for his confidence. 

My interest has always revolved around my family and my career. However, I love to travel & explore the other side of the world, but had very few travels so far.
